OL,7,FA man stabbed his stepdaughter and her
OL,8,Fhusband to death "in quick succession"
OL,9,Fat their home after he "just lost it",
OL,10,Fa court has heard.
OL,12,FParents-of-four Josh Bashford, 33, and
OL,13,FChloe Bashford, 30, were found dead at
OL,14,Ftheir home in Newhaven, East Sussex,
OL,15,Fon June 9 2023.
OL,17,FDerek Martin, 67, from Brighton,
OL,18,Fadmitted manslaughter of the couple in
OL,19,FAugust 2023, but denies murder.
