OL,7,FOn Monday, jurors at Brighton Law
OL,8,FCourts heard there is "no dispute"
OL,9,Fabout whether Martin killed the
OL,10,Fcouple, but he claims diminished
OL,11,Fresponsibility, arguing that he was
OL,12,Fsuffering an "abnormality of mental
OL,13,Ffunctioning" at the time.
OL,15,FMartin and Mrs Bashford had spent the
OL,16,Fmorning together before he attacked
OL,17,Fher with a hammer and stabbed her
OL,18,Feight times just after midday
