OL,7,FHe then ambushed Mr Bashford, who had
OL,8,Fbeen driving home from work, and
OL,9,Fchased him into an upstairs bedroom
OL,10,Fbefore stabbing and ligaturing him.
OL,12,FThat afternoon, Martin met their four
OL,13,Fchildren at a coffee shop and dropped
OL,14,Fthem at their grandmother's house,
OL,15,Fbefore turning himself in at Brighton
OL,16,Fpolice station.
