OL,7,FProsecuting, Julian Evans KC said:
OL,8,F"Chloe and Joshua were attacked and
OL,9,Fkilled in quick succession. Both
OL,10,Fattacks took place inside their home
OL,11,Faddress.
OL,13,F"Chloe was attacked first. When she
OL,14,Fwas attacked, Chloe and Derek Martin
OL,15,Fwere in the house together. Josh was
OL,16,Fnot there at the time, he was about to
OL,17,Farrive at home.
