OL,7,F"At about 12:16, just after a quarter
OL,8,Fpast midday, Derek Martin attacked
OL,9,FChloe with a hammer. He hit her with
OL,10,Fthe hammer on the top of her head.
OL,12,F"Then he went to the kitchen to
OL,13,Fretrieve a large knife and having done
OL,14,Fso, he then repeatedly stabbed Chloe
OL,15,Fwith that knife, causing severe
OL,16,Finjuries from which she died.
