OL,7,F"At about 12:20, Josh arrived home.
OL,8,FJust after he entered the house, Derek
OL,9,FMartin attacked him. In the course of
OL,10,Fthe attack, Derek Martin repeatedly
OL,11,Fstabbed Josh with a knife and
OL,12,Fcompressed his neck with a ligature,
OL,13,Fcausing injuries from which he too
OL,14,Fdied."
OL,16,FMartin removed the handles from the
OL,17,Fbedroom doors the bodies were lying
OL,18,Fin, changed his clothes, and took the
OL,19,Fdoorbell camera off the front door,
OL,20,Fthe court heard.
