OL,10,Fhe met the other children.
OL,12,FLater, after stopping to dispose of
OL,13,FMrs Bashford's phone and dropping off
OL,14,Fthe children, he went into the police
OL,15,Fstation and said: "I've murdered two
OL,16,Fpeople."
