OL,7,FWhile Martin was not still in a
OL,8,Frelationship with Mrs Bashford's
OL,9,Fmother, he had stayed "close friends"
OL,10,Fwith his stepdaughter, and she
OL,11,Freferred to him as "step dad" in a
OL,12,Ftext to her friend the day she died,
OL,13,Fthe court heard.
OL,15,FHer eldest son described Martin as a
OL,16,F"grandfather figure" and said he was
OL,17,F"easy to be around", but added that he
OL,18,Fhad a "bad temper" and could "switch
OL,19,Fup" easily.
