OL,7,FMartin first admitted being
OL,8,Fresponsible for the killings in police
OL,9,Finterview on June 10 2023.
OL,11,FMr Evans recounted the interview in
OL,12,Fcourt: "He said that he felt he was
OL,13,Fgetting 'used' all of the time. He
OL,14,Fcould not do enough for people, and he
OL,15,Fhad got into a lot of debt himself as
OL,16,Fwell.
OL,18,F"Then he said that he 'just lost it'
OL,19,Fand he 'just flipped'. He hit Chloe on
OL,20,Fthe head with the hammer. He did not
OL,21,Fknow what had happened.
