OL,7,F"He said that Josh came in the door.
OL,8,FHe (Martin) was behind the door. He
OL,9,Fsaid that Josh saw him with the knife
OL,10,Fin his hand and he ran upstairs.
OL,12,F"Martin followed Josh upstairs and
OL,13,FJosh ran into the bedroom.
OL,15,F"He said that he remembered stabbing
OL,16,FJosh. He stabbed him somewhere in the
OL,17,Ffront of his body. He did not know how
