OL,7,FFive psychiatrists have been
OL,8,Finstructed to assess whether Martin
OL,9,Fcan use the diminished responsibility
OL,10,Fdefence.
OL,12,FAll of them have reported Martin as
OL,13,Fhaving a depressive disorder at the
OL,14,Ftime of the attacks, but there is
OL,15,Fdispute about the severity and whether
OL,16,Fit reduces his culpability for the
OL,17,Fkillings.
OL,19,FThe trial continues and is due to last
OL,20,Fthree weeks.
